css_definition: @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Josefin Sans'); body, .form {font-family: Josefin Sans !important; font-weight: 800 !important; font-size: 16px;} .bg-primary {background-color: black !important;} div.form {border: 0px solid lightgrey !important} .navbar-dark .navbar-nav .nav-link {color: white !important} .navbar-dark .navbar-nav .nav-link.active {color: yellow !important} p {background: linear-gradient(45deg, black, black);}
